  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The principal manifestation of hemorrhoidal disease is bleeding; however the severity
      evaluation is today based on prolapsus (Goligher classification) and bleeding factor is not
      included.

      Even if there was some rare score including bleeding in literature , none of them were
      validated.

      The aim of the study is first validation of bleeding score .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
